ni) 提起诉讼后为她辩护的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/America-Ferrera-Amber-Tamblyn-Blake-Lively-and-Alexis-Bledel.-CREDIT_-Andrew-Toth_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/America-Ferrera-Amber-Tamblyn-Blake-Lively-and-Alexis-Bledel.-CREDIT_-Andrew-Toth_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/America-Ferrera-Amber-Tamblyn-Blake-Lively-and-Alexis-Bledel.-CREDIT_-Andrew-Toth_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/America-Ferrera-Amber-Tamblyn-Blake-Lively-and-Alexis-Bledel.-CREDIT_-Andrew-Toth_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/America-Ferrera-Amber-Tamblyn-Blake-Lively-and-Alexis-Bledel.-CREDIT_-Andrew-Toth_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/America-Ferrera-Amber-Tamblyn-Blake-Lively-and-Alexis-Bledel.-CREDIT_-Andrew-Toth_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/America-Ferrera-Amber-Tamblyn-Blake-Lively-and-Alexis-Bledel.-CREDIT_-Andrew-Toth_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blake-lively">布莱克·莱弗利 (Blake Lively</a> ) 起诉<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/it-ends-with-us"><i>《与我们同在》</i></a>主演兼导演贾斯汀·巴尔多尼 (Justin Baldoni) 性骚扰后，她<em>在《旅行裤姐妹会》中的联合主演</em>公开为她辩护。</p><p>周五（12月20日）， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/blake-lively-sues-it-ends-with-us-co-star-justin-baldoni-over-severe-emotional-distress-3824279">莱弗利对她的前搭档提出了性骚扰和报复投诉</a>。据<a href="https://www.tmz.com/2024/12/21/blake-lively-sues-justin-baldoni-sexual-harassment-retaliation-on-it-ends-with-us-set/?adid=social-tw" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>TMZ</i></a>报道，诉讼称巴尔多尼的行为导致莱弗利“严重情绪困扰”。</p><p>现在，莱弗利的“朋友和姐妹”亚美莉卡·费雷拉 (America Ferrera)、艾波·坦布林 (Amber Tamblyn) 和亚历克西斯·布莱德尔 (Alexis Bledel)（与她共同主演了 2005 年电影及其 2008 年续集）已通过 Instagram 发表声明支持她。</p><p>三人写道：“我们与她站在一起，对据报道的旨在破坏她声誉的活动进行反击。” “在<em>《与我们同在》</em>的整个拍摄过程中，我们看到她鼓起勇气为自己和片场的同事要求一个安全的工作场所，我们震惊地看到有预谋和报复性的努力，从而抹黑了她的声音。</p><p>声明继续说道：“最令人不安的是，公然利用家庭暴力幸存者的故事来压制寻求安全的妇女。” “这种虚伪令人震惊。令我们震惊的现实是，即使一个女性像我们的朋友布莱克一样坚强、有名气、资源丰富，但她也可能因为敢于要求安全的工作环境而面临强力报复。”</p><p>费雷拉、坦布林和布莱德尔继续鼓励其他人阅读<a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2024/12/21/business/media/blake-lively-justin-baldoni-it-ends-with-us.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《纽约时报》</em></a>上详细介绍的完整法律投诉。 “我们姐姐为自己和他人挺身而出的勇气激励了我们，”他们补充道。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DD5oh80OduT/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148